<Layout title="Notes • Zugarek" description="Short-form notes, quick fixes, and links worth keeping.">
  <section class="card prose">
    <h1>Notes</h1>
    <p class="muted">Short, searchable entries. If it’s not worth a full project page, it goes here.</p>

    <h2>What belongs here</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>One-off fixes</li>
      <li>Part numbers</li>
      <li>Commands you always forget</li>
      <li>Links to documentation</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="muted">Create a project page when the story matters; create a note when only the answer matters.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
